<h3>Meta Tag Keywords</h3><p>Keywords should be related to what you are selling on your website.&nbsp;            Separate each keyword with a comma.&nbsp; Keywords will help to increase            your search engine rankings.&nbsp; Do not get carried away though.&nbsp;            Using too many keywords will hurt your ranking.&nbsp; Try to use about            20 to 25 keywords that describe your website.&nbsp; Do not repeat words            more than 3 times.</p>




